<p><a name="-mang-nhieu-chieu"></a></p>

<h2 id="20-m·∫£ng-nhi·ªÅu-chi·ªÅu">2.0. M·∫£ng nhi·ªÅu chi·ªÅu</h2>
<p>Trong Numpy, ng∆∞·ªùi ta th∆∞·ªùng d√πng m·∫£ng numpy hai chi·ªÅu ƒë·ªÉ th·ªÉ hi·ªán m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n. M·∫£ng hai chi·ªÅu c√≥ th·ªÉ coi l√† m·ªôt m·∫£ng c·ªßa c√°c m·∫£ng m·ªôt chi·ªÅu. Trong ƒë√≥, m·ªói <em>m·∫£ng nh·ªè m·ªôt chi·ªÅu</em> t∆∞∆°ng ·ª©ng v·ªõi m·ªôt h√†ng c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n.</p>

<p>N√≥i c√°ch kh√°c, ma tr·∫≠n c√≥ th·ªÉ ƒë∆∞·ª£c coi l√† m·∫£ng c·ªßa c√°c vector h√†ng - m·ªói vector h√†ng ƒë∆∞·ª£c bi·ªÉu di·ªÖn b·∫±ng m·ªôt m·∫£ng numpy m·ªôt chi·ªÅu.</p>

<hr />

<div class="imgcap">
<img src="/assets/fundaml/matrix.png" align="center" width="400" />
</div>
<hr />

<p>V√≠ d·ª•, n·∫øu m·ªôt m·∫£ng numpy hai chi·ªÅu <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">a</code> m√¥ t·∫£ ma tr·∫≠n:
\(\left[
\begin{matrix} 1 &amp; 2 \\ 3 &amp; 4 \end{matrix} \right]
\), khi ƒë∆∞·ª£c in ra n√≥ s·∫Ω c√≥ d·∫°ng:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">]])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>·ªû ƒë√¢y ch√∫ng ta c√≥ th·ªÉ nh√¨n th·∫•y ba m·∫£ng, m·ªói m·∫£ng ƒë∆∞·ª£c th·ªÉ hi·ªán b·∫±ng m·ªôt c·∫∑p 
ƒë√≥ng m·ªü ngo·∫∑c vu√¥ng <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">[]</code>:</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>hai m·∫£ng <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">[1, 2]</code> v√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">[3, 4]</code> th·ªÉ hi·ªán c√°c h√†ng c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n. Ch√∫ng l√† c√°c 
m·∫£ng m·ªôt chi·ªÅu.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>m·∫£ng <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">[[1, 2], [3, 4]]</code> c√≥ hai ph√¢n t·ª≠, m·ªói ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ l√† m·ªôt h√†ng c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n.</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p>Theo quy ∆∞·ªõc c·ªßa Numpy, ch√∫ng ta c·∫ßn ƒëi t·ª´ m·∫£ng ngo√†i c√πng t·ªõi c√°c m·∫£ng trong:</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>m·∫£ng l·ªõn nh·∫•t l√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">[[1, 2], [3, 4]]</code> ƒë∆∞·ª£c coi l√† m·∫£ng ·ª©ng v·ªõi <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">axis = 0</code>. 
Trong m·∫£ng n√†y, th√†nh ph·∫ßn th·ª© nh·∫•t l√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">[1, 2]</code>, th√†nh ph·∫ßn th·ª© hai l√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">[3, 4]</code>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>hai m·∫£ng l·ªõn th·ª© hai l√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">[1, 2]</code> v√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">[3, 4]</code> ƒë∆∞·ª£c coi l√† c√°c m·∫£ng ·ª©ng v·ªõi <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">axis = 1</code>.</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p>(Xem th√™m h√¨nh v·∫Ω b√™n.)</p>

<p><strong>Ch√∫ √Ω:</strong></p>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>M·ªôt m·∫£ng numpy ho√†n to√†n c√≥ th·ªÉ c√≥ nhi·ªÅu h∆°n hai chi·ªÅu. Khi ƒë√≥ ta v·∫´n ƒëi t·ª´ 
c·∫∑p ngo·∫∑c vu√¥ng ngo√†i c√πng v√†o t·ªõi trong c√πng, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">axis</code> c≈©ng ƒëi t·ª´ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">0, 1, ...</code> 
theo th·ª© t·ª± ƒë√≥.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>M·ªói <em>m·∫£ng con</em> ph·∫£i c√≥ s·ªë ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ b·∫±ng nhau, th·ªÉ hi·ªán cho vi·ªác m·ªói h√†ng c·ªßa 
ma tr·∫≠n ph·∫£i c√≥ s·ªë chi·ªÅu nh∆∞ nhau, kh√¥ng c√≥ h√†ng n√†o <em>th√≤ ra th·ª•t v√†o</em>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Khi l√†m vi·ªác v·ªõi c√°c th∆∞ vi·ªán cho Machine Learning, m·ªói ƒëi·ªÉm d·ªØ li·ªáu th∆∞·ªùng 
ƒë∆∞·ª£c coi l√† m·ªôt m·∫£ng m·ªôt chi·ªÅu. T·∫≠p h·ª£p c√°c ƒëi·ªÉm d·ªØ li·ªáu th∆∞·ªùng ƒë∆∞·ª£c l∆∞u trong 
m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n - t·ª©c m·∫£ng c·ªßa c√°c m·∫£ng m·ªôt chi·ªÅu. Trong ma tr·∫≠n n√†y, m·ªói <strong>h√†ng</strong> 
t∆∞∆°ng ·ª©ng v·ªõi m·ªôt ƒëi·ªÉm d·ªØ li·ªáu.</p>
  </li>
</ol>

<p>Vi·ªác n√†y h∆°i ng∆∞·ª£c v·ªõi c√°ch x√¢y d·ª±ng to√°n h·ªçc c·ªßa c√°c thu·∫≠t to√°n, n∆°i m√† m·ªói 
ƒëi·ªÉm d·ªØ li·ªáu th∆∞·ªùng ƒë∆∞·ª£c coi l√† m·ªôt vector c·ªôt - t·ª©c m·ªói <strong>c·ªôt</strong> c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n l√† 
m·ªôt ƒëi·ªÉm d·ªØ li·ªáu. Khi ƒë·ªçc c√°c t√†i li·ªáu v√† l√†m vi·ªác v·ªõi c√°c th∆∞ vi·ªán, b·∫°n ƒë·ªçc c·∫ßn 
ch√∫ √Ω.</p>

<p>Gi·ªëng nh∆∞ b√†i ‚ÄúC∆° b·∫£n v·ªÅ vector‚Äù, trong b√†i h·ªçc n√†y, ch√∫ng ta s·∫Ω c√πng l√†m quen 
v·ªõi c√°c c√°ch x·ª≠ l√Ω ma tr·∫≠n trong Numpy: Kh·ªüi t·∫°o, truy c·∫≠p, thay ƒë·ªïi, ma tr·∫≠n 
ƒë·∫∑c bi·ªát, ‚Ä¶</p>

<p><a name="-khoi-tao-mot-ma-tran"></a></p>

<h2 id="21-kh·ªüi-t·∫°o-m·ªôt-ma-tr·∫≠n">2.1. Kh·ªüi t·∫°o m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n</h2>
<p><a name="-khoi-tao-mot-ma-tran-1"></a></p>

<h3 id="211-kh·ªüi-t·∫°o-m·ªôt-ma-tr·∫≠n">2.1.1. Kh·ªüi t·∫°o m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n</h3>
<p>C√°ch ƒë∆°n gi·∫£n nh·∫•t ƒë·ªÉ kh·ªüi t·∫°o m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n l√† nh·∫≠p v√†o t·ª´ng ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n 
ƒë√≥. C√°ch l√†m n√†y, t·∫•t nhi√™n, ch·ªâ ph√π h·ª£p v·ªõi c√°c ma tr·∫≠n nh·ªè.</p>
<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">numpy</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">np</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">]])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<p><em>N·∫øu b·∫°n m·ªõi chuy·ªÉn t·ª´ Matlab qua Python, b·∫°n s·∫Ω th·∫•y c√°ch khai b√°o c·ªßa Matlab <strong>d·ªÖ ch·ªãu</strong> h∆°n r·∫•t nhi·ªÅu. Ch√∫ng ta s·∫Ω ph·∫£i quen d·∫ßn th√¥i :).</em></p>

<p>Khi khai b√°o m·ªôt m·∫£ng numpy n√≥i chung, n·∫øu <em>√≠t nh·∫•t m·ªôt</em> ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ c·ªßa m·∫£ng l√† 
<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">float</code>, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">type</code> c·ªßa m·ªçi ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ trong m·∫£ng s·∫Ω ƒë∆∞·ª£c coi l√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">'numpy.float64'</code> 
(s·ªë th·ª±c 64 bit).</p>

<p>Ng∆∞·ª£c l·∫°i, n·∫øu to√†n b·ªô c√°c ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ l√† s·ªë nguy√™n (kh√¥ng c√≥ d·∫•u <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">.</code> xu·∫•t hi·ªán),
<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">type</code> c·ªßa m·ªçi ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ trong m·∫£ng s·∫Ω ƒë∆∞·ª£c coi l√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">'numpy.int64'</code> (s·ªë nguy√™n 64 bit).</p>

<p>N·∫øu mu·ªën ch·ªâ ƒë·ªãnh <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">type</code> c·ªßa c√°c ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ trong m·∫£ng, ta c·∫ßn ƒë·∫∑t gi√° tr·ªã cho <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">dtype</code>. 
V√≠ d·ª•:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">B</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">]],</span> <span class="n">dtype</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">float</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="nb">type</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">B</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])</span>
<span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="nb">type</span> <span class="s">'numpy.float64'</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<hr />

<p><strong>B√†i t·∫≠p:</strong></p>

<p>Khai b√°o m·ªôt m·∫£ng numpy hai chi·ªÅu <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code> m√¥ t·∫£ ma tr·∫≠n:</p>

<p>\[\mathbf{A} = \left[
\begin{matrix}
1 &amp; 2 &amp; 3 \\ 4 &amp; 5 &amp; 6 \\ 7 &amp; 8 &amp; 9
\end{matrix}
\right]
\]</p>

<hr />

<p><a name="-ma-tran-don-vi-va-ma-tran-duong-cheo"></a></p>

<h2 id="22-ma-tr·∫≠n-ƒë∆°n-v·ªã-v√†-ma-tr·∫≠n-ƒë∆∞·ªùng-ch√©o">2.2. Ma tr·∫≠n ƒë∆°n v·ªã v√† ma tr·∫≠n ƒë∆∞·ªùng ch√©o</h2>
<p><a name="-ma-tran-don-vi"></a></p>

<h3 id="221-ma-tr·∫≠n-ƒë∆°n-v·ªã">2.2.1. Ma tr·∫≠n ƒë∆°n v·ªã</h3>

<p>ƒê·ªÉ t·∫°o m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n ƒë∆°n v·ªã c√≥ s·ªë chi·ªÅu b·∫±ng <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">n</code> (ma tr·∫≠n ƒë∆°n v·ªã l√† m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n vu√¥ng c√≥ t·∫•t c·∫£ c√°c ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ tr√™n ƒë∆∞·ªùng ch√©o b·∫±ng 1), ch√∫ng ta s·ª≠ d·ª•ng h√†m <a href="https://docs.scipy.org/doc/numpy-1.13.0/reference/generated/numpy.eye.html"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">np.eye()</code></a>:</p>
<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">numpy</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">np</span> 
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">eye</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span> <span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">]])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>H√†m <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">np.eye()</code> c≈©ng ƒë∆∞·ª£c d√πng ƒë·ªÉ t·∫°o c√°c ma tr·∫≠n to√†n 1 ·ªü m·ªôt ƒë∆∞·ªùng ch√©o ph·ª• n√†o ƒë√≥, c√°c th√†nh ph·∫ßn c√≤n l·∫°i b·∫±ng 0. V√≠ d·ª•:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">eye</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">k</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span> <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">eye</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">k</span><span class="o">=</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span> <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">]])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">k = 1</code> s·∫Ω t∆∞∆°ng ·ª©ng v·ªõi ƒë∆∞·ªùng ch√©o ph·ª• ngay <em>tr√™n</em> ƒë∆∞·ªùng ch√©o ch√≠h. <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">k = -2</code> s·∫Ω t∆∞∆°ng ·ª©ng v·ªõi ƒë∆∞·ªùng ch√©o ph·ª• th·ª© hai <em>b√™n d∆∞·ªõi</em> ƒë∆∞·ªùng ch√©o ch√≠nh.</p>

<p>B·∫°n ƒë·ªçc c√≥ th·ªÉ ƒë·ªçc th√™m v·ªÅ c√°ch s·ª≠ d·ª•ng h√†m ‚Äònp.eye()‚Äô <a href="https://docs.scipy.org/doc/numpy-1.13.0/reference/generated/numpy.eye.html">t·∫°i ƒë√¢y</a>.</p>

<p><em>Xin nh·∫Øc l·∫°i r·∫±ng b·∫°n ƒë·ªçc lu√¥n c√≥ th·ªÉ xem c√°ch s·ª≠ d·ª•ng m·ªôt h√†m tr√™n terminal b·∫±ng c√°ch g√µ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">help(func)</code> trong ƒë√≥ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">func</code> l√† t√™n h√†m b·∫°n mu·ªën tra c·ª©u. V√≠ d·ª•, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">help(np.eye)</code>.</em></p>

<p><a name="-ma-tran-duong-cheo"></a></p>

<h3 id="222-ma-tr·∫≠n-ƒë∆∞·ªùng-ch√©o">2.2.2. Ma tr·∫≠n ƒë∆∞·ªùng ch√©o</h3>
<p>ƒê·ªÉ khai b√°o m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n ƒë∆∞·ªùng ch√©o, ho·∫∑c mu·ªën tr√≠ch xu·∫•t ƒë∆∞·ªùng ch√©o c·ªßa m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n, ta d√πng h√†m <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">np.diag</code>.</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">diag</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">])</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">diag</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">diag</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">]))</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>N·∫øu ƒë·∫ßu v√†o l√† m·ªôt m·∫£ng m·ªôt chi·ªÅu, tr·∫£ v·ªÅ m·ªôt m·∫£ng hai chi·ªÅu th·ªÉ hi·ªán ma tr·∫≠n c√≥ ƒë∆∞·ªùng ch√©o l√† c√°c ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ thu·ªôc m·∫£ng ƒë√≥.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>N·∫øu ƒë·∫ßu v√†o l√† m·ªôt m·∫£ng hai chi·ªÅu (c√≥ th·ªÉ kh√¥ng vu√¥ng), tr·∫£ v·ªÅ m·∫£ng m·ªôt chi·ªÅu ch·ª©a c√°c gi√° tr·ªã ·ªü h√†ng th·ª© <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">i</code>, 
c·ªôt th·ª© <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">i</code> v·ªõi <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">0 &lt;= i &lt;= min(m, n)</code>. Trong ƒë√≥ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">m</code>, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">n</code> l·∫ßn l∆∞·ª£t l√† s·ªë h√†ng v√† s·ªë c·ªôt c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n ƒë∆∞·ª£c bi·ªÉu di·ªÖn b·∫±ng m·∫£ng hai chi·ªÅu ban ƒë·∫ßu.</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p><em>ƒê∆∞·ªùng ch√©o ph·ª•</em> c·ªßa m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n c≈©ng c√≥ th·ªÉ ƒë∆∞·ª£c l·∫•y b·∫±ng c√°ch s·ª≠ d·ª•ng h√†m n√†y v√† ch·ªâ ra gi√° tr·ªã c·ªßa <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">k</code>:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">a</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">8</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">9</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">a</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">8</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">9</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">diag</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">a</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">k</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<hr />

<p><strong>B√†i t·∫≠p:</strong></p>

<p>V·ªõi m·ªôt s·ªë t·ª± nhi√™n <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">n</code>, h√£y vi·∫øt h√†m tr·∫£ v·ªÅ ma tr·∫≠n c√≥ d·∫°ng: 
\[
\left[
\begin{matrix}
0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; \dots &amp; 0 &amp; 0 \\ 1 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; \dots &amp; 0 &amp; 0 \\ 0 &amp; 2 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; \dots &amp; 0 &amp; 0 \\ \dots &amp; \dots &amp; \dots &amp; \dots &amp; \ddots &amp; \dots \\ 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; \dots &amp; 0 &amp; 0 \\ 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 &amp; \dots &amp; n &amp; 0 
\end{matrix}
\right]
\]
t·ª©c ƒë∆∞·ªùng ch√©o ph·ª• ngay d∆∞·ªõi ƒë∆∞·ªùng ch√©o ch√≠nh nh·∫≠n c√°c gi√° tr·ªã t·ª´ 1 ƒë·∫øn \(n\). C√°c th√†nh ph·∫ßn l√† ki·ªÉu s·ªë nguy√™n.</p>

<hr />

<p><a name="-kich-thuoc-cua-ma-tran"></a></p>

<h2 id="23-k√≠ch-th∆∞·ªõc-c·ªßa-ma-tr·∫≠n">2.3. K√≠ch th∆∞·ªõc c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n</h2>

<p>Gi·ªëng nh∆∞ c√°ch t√¨m k√≠ch th∆∞·ªõc c·ªßa m·∫£ng m·ªôt chi·ªÉu, ƒë·ªÉ t√¨m k√≠ch th∆∞·ªõc c·ªßa m·∫£ng hai chi·ªÅu, ta c≈©ng s·ª≠ d·ª•ng thu·ªôc t√≠nh <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">shape</code>:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">numpy</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">np</span> 
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">8</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">9</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">10</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">11</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">12</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">8</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mi">9</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">10</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">11</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">12</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">shape</span>
<span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">)</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>·ªû ƒë√¢y, k·∫øt qu·∫£ tr·∫£ v·ªÅ l√† m·ªôt <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">tuple</code>. S·ªë ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ c·ªßa tuple n√†y ch√≠nh l√† s·ªë 
chi·ªÅu c·ªßa m·∫£ng. N·∫øu coi m·∫£ng hai chi·ªÅu nh∆∞ ma tr·∫≠n, s·ªë h√†ng v√† s·ªë c·ªôt c·ªßa ma 
tr·∫≠n c√≥ th·ªÉ ƒë∆∞·ª£c t√≠nh b·∫±ng:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">shape</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span>
<span class="mi">3</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">shape</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span>
<span class="mi">4</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>V·ªõi m·∫£ng numpy nhi·ªÅu chi·ªÅu, ta c≈©ng d√πng thu·ªôc t√≠nh <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">shape</code> ƒë·ªÉ t√¨m k√≠ch th∆∞·ªõc 
c·ªßa m·ªói chi·ªÅu.</p>

<p><a name="-truy-cap-vao-tung-phan-tu-cua-ma-tran"></a></p>

<h2 id="24-truy-c·∫≠p-v√†o-t·ª´ng-ph·∫ßn-t·ª≠-c·ªßa-ma-tr·∫≠n">2.4. Truy c·∫≠p v√†o t·ª´ng ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n</h2>

<p><a name="-truy-cap-vao-tung-phan-tu"></a></p>

<h3 id="241-truy-c·∫≠p-v√†o-t·ª´ng-ph·∫ßn-t·ª≠">2.4.1. Truy c·∫≠p v√†o t·ª´ng ph·∫ßn t·ª≠</h3>
<p>C√≥ hai c√°ch ƒë·ªÉ truy c·∫≠p v√†o m·ªói ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ c·ªßa m·∫£ng hai chi·ªÅu:
<a name="-cach--giong-voi-list"></a></p>

<h4 id="2411-c√°ch-1-gi·ªëng-v·ªõi-list">2.4.1.1. C√°ch 1: gi·ªëng v·ªõi list</h4>
<p>ƒê·ªÉ truy c·∫≠p v√†o ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ ·ªü h√†ng th·ª© <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">i</code>, c·ªôt th·ª© <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">j</code> c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n (ch·ªâ s·ªë b·∫Øt ƒë·∫ßu 
t·ª´ 0), ta c√≥ th·ªÉ coi ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ ƒë√≥ l√† ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ th·ª© <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">j</code> c·ªßa m·∫£ng <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">i</code> trong m·∫£ng hai 
chi·ªÅu ban ƒë·∫ßu.</p>

<p>V√≠ d·ª•:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">numpy</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">np</span> 
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">8</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">9</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">]</span>
<span class="mi">6</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>·ªü ƒë√¢y <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A[1]</code> ch√≠nh l·∫£ m·∫£ng m·ªôt chi·ªÅu <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">[4, 5, 6]</code>, trong m·∫£ng n√†y, ta l·∫•y ph·∫ßn 
t·ª≠ c√≥ ch·ªâ s·ªë l√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">2</code>, ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ ƒë√≥ c√≥ gi√° tr·ªã l√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">6</code>. V·∫≠y <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A[1][2]</code> = 6.</p>

<p><a name="-cach--giong-nhu-matlab"></a></p>

<h4 id="2412-c√°ch-2-gi·ªëng-nh∆∞-matlab">2.4.1.2. C√°ch 2: gi·ªëng nh∆∞ Matlab</h4>
<p>Trong Matlab, ƒë·ªÉ truy c·∫≠p v√†o ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ ·ªü h√†ng ƒë·∫ßu ti√™n, c·ªôt ƒë·∫ßu ti√™n c·ªßa m·ªôt ma 
tr·∫≠n <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code>, ta s·ª≠ d·ª•ng <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A(1, 1)</code>. Trong Numpy, c√≥ m·ªôt ch√∫t thay ƒë·ªïi:</p>

<ol>
  <li>Ch·ªâ s·ªë b·∫Øt ƒë·∫ßu t·ª´ 0.</li>
  <li>B·ªô ch·ªâ s·ªë ƒë∆∞·ª£c ƒë·∫∑t trong d·∫•u ngo·∫∑c vu√¥ng <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">[]</code>.</li>
</ol>

<p>V√≠ d·ª•</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span>
<span class="mi">8</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><a name="-truy-cap-vao-hangcot"></a></p>

<h3 id="242-truy-c·∫≠p-v√†o-h√†ngc·ªôt">2.4.2. Truy c·∫≠p v√†o h√†ng/c·ªôt</h3>

<p>ƒê·ªÉ truy c·∫≠p v√†o h√†ng c√≥ ch·ªâ s·ªë <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">i</code> c·ªßa m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code>, ta ch·ªâ c·∫ßn d√πng <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A[i]</code> 
ho·∫∑c <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A[i,:]</code> ho·∫∑c <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A[i][:]</code>:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">]</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">8</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">9</span><span class="p">])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,:]</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>ƒê·ªÉ truy c·∫≠p v√†o c·ªôt c√≥ ch·ªâ s·ªë <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">j</code>, ta d√πng <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A[:,j]</code>:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span><span class="p">[:,</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">8</span><span class="p">])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><strong>Ch√∫ √Ω:</strong></p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>Trong Numpy, k·∫øt qu·∫£ tr·∫£ v·ªÅ c·ªßa m·ªôt c·ªôt hay h√†ng ƒë·ªÅu l√† m·ªôt m·∫£ng m·ªôt chi·ªÅu, 
kh√¥ng ph·∫£i l√† m·ªôt vector c·ªôt nh∆∞ trong Matlab. Tuy nhi√™n, khi l·∫•y m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n 
nh√¢n v·ªõi n√≥, n√≥ v·∫´n ƒë∆∞·ª£c coi l√† m·ªôt vector c·ªôt. Th√¥ng tin chi ti·∫øt s·∫Ω c√≥ trong 
c√°c b√†i sau.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>N·∫øu s·ª≠ d·ª•ng <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A[:][1]</code>, k·∫øt qu·∫£ tr·∫£ v·ªÅ l√† <strong>h√†ng</strong> c√≥ ch·ªâ s·ªë <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">1</code> ch·ª© kh√¥ng 
ph·∫£i c·ªôt c√≥ ch·ªâ s·ªë <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">1</code>. Trong tr∆∞·ªùng h·ª£p n√†y, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A[:]</code> v·∫´n ƒë∆∞·ª£c hi·ªÉu l√† c·∫£ ma 
tr·∫≠n <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code>, v√¨ v·∫≠y n√™n <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A[:][1]</code> t∆∞∆°ng ƒë∆∞∆°ng v·ªõi <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A[1]</code>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>C√≥ s·ª± kh√°c nhau cƒÉn b·∫£n gi·ªØa <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code> v√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A[:]</code>, ch√∫ng ta s·∫Ω quay l·∫°i trong m·ªôt 
b√†i n√†o ƒë√≥ ·ªü sau.</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<hr />

<p><strong>B√†i t·∫≠p:</strong></p>

<p>Cho m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code>, vi·∫øt h√†m <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">myfunc</code> t√≠nh t·ªïng c√°c ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ tr√™n c√°c <strong>c·ªôt</strong> 
c√≥ ch·ªâ s·ªë ch·∫µn (<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">0, 2, 4, ...</code>) c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n ƒë√≥. 
V√≠ d·ª•:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">myfunc</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="mi">4</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>Gi·∫£i th√≠ch: c·ªôt c√≥ ch·ªâ s·ªë <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">0</code> c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n l√† m·∫£ng <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">[1, 3]</code>, t·ªïng c√°c ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ 
c·ªßa m·∫£ng n√†y l√† 4.</p>

<hr />

<p><a name="-truy-cap-vao-nhieu-phan-tu-cua-ma-tran"></a></p>

<h2 id="25-truy-c·∫≠p-v√†o-nhi·ªÅu-ph·∫ßn-t·ª≠-c·ªßa-ma-tr·∫≠n">2.5. Truy c·∫≠p v√†o nhi·ªÅu ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n</h2>
<p><a name="-nhieu-phan-tu-trong-cung-mot-hang"></a></p>

<h3 id="251-nhi·ªÅu-ph·∫ßn-t·ª≠-trong-c√πng-m·ªôt-h√†ng">2.5.1. Nhi·ªÅu ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ trong c√πng m·ªôt h√†ng</h3>
<p>Vi·ªác truy c·∫≠p v√†o nhi·ªÅu ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ trong m·ªôt h√†ng t∆∞∆°ng t·ª± nh∆∞ v·ªõi m·∫£ng m·ªôt chi·ªÅu:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">numpy</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">np</span> 
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">8</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">9</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">10</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">11</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">12</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">8</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mi">9</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">10</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">11</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">12</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">:]</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nb">range</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">A</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">shape</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">)]</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>trong ƒë√≥, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">range(0, A.shape[1], 2)</code> t·∫°o ra m·ªôt <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">list</code> c√°c ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ l√† c·∫•p s·ªë c·ªông v·ªõi c√¥ng sai l√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">2</code>, 
b·∫Øt ƒë·∫ßu t·ª´ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">0</code> v√† k·∫øt th√∫c t·∫°i s·ªë l·ªõn nh·∫•t c√≥ th·ªÉ kh√¥ng v∆∞·ª£t qu√° s·ªë c·ªôt c·ªßa <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code>. S·ªë c·ªôt c·ªßa <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code> ch√≠nh l√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A.shape[1]</code>.</p>

<p><a name="-nhieu-phan-tu-trong-cung-mot-cot"></a></p>

<h3 id="252-nhi·ªÅu-ph·∫ßn-t·ª≠-trong-c√πng-m·ªôt-c·ªôt">2.5.2. Nhi·ªÅu ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ trong c√πng m·ªôt c·ªôt</h3>
<p>T∆∞∆°ng t·ª± v·ªõi nhi·ªÅu ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ trong c√πng m·ªôt c·ªôt:</p>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>&gt;&gt;&gt; A[[0, 2], -1] # the first and the third elements in the last column
array([ 4, 12])
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><a name="-nhieu-hang-nhieu-cot"></a></p>

<h3 id="253-nhi·ªÅu-h√†ng-nhi·ªÅu-c·ªôt">2.5.3. Nhi·ªÅu h√†ng, nhi·ªÅu c·ªôt</h3>
<p>N·∫øu mu·ªën <em>tr√≠ch</em> m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n con t·ª´ ma tr·∫≠n ban ƒë·∫ßu, gi·∫£ s·ª≠ l·∫•y ma tr·∫≠n ƒë∆∞·ª£c 
t·∫°o b·ªüi h√†ng c√≥ ch·ªâ s·ªë <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">1</code> v√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">2</code>, c·ªôt c√≥ ch·ªâ s·ªë <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">0</code> v√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">3</code>, ta l√†m nh∆∞ sau:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span><span class="p">[[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">]][:,</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">]]</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">8</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mi">9</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">12</span><span class="p">]])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><strong>Ch√∫ √Ω:</strong> M·ªôt c√°ch t·ª± nhi√™n, b·∫°n ƒë·ªçc c√≥ th·ªÉ suy ra r·∫±ng c√¢u l·ªánh n√™n l√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A[[1, 
2], [0, 3]]</code> (gi·ªëng nh∆∞ c√°ch l√†m trong Matlab). Tuy nhi√™n, c√¢u l·ªánh n√†y s·∫Ω cho 
ra m·ªôt k·∫øt qu·∫£ kh√°c (xem m·ª•c 4).</p>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A[[1, 2]][:, [0,3]]</code> c√≥ th·ªÉ hi·ªÉu ƒë∆∞·ª£c l√†: ƒë·∫ßu ti√™n l·∫•y hai h√†ng c√≥ ch·ªâ s·ªë <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">1</code> 
v√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">2</code> b·∫±ng <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A[[1, 2]]</code>, ta ƒë∆∞·ª£c m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n, sau ƒë√≥ l·∫•y hai c·ªôt c√≥ ch·ªâ s·ªë <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">0</code> 
v√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">3</code> c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n m·ªõi n√†y.
<a name="-cap-cac-toa-do"></a></p>

<h3 id="254-c·∫∑p-c√°c-to·∫°-ƒë·ªô">2.5.4. C·∫∑p c√°c to·∫° ƒë·ªô</h3>

<p>X√©t c√¢u l·ªánh:</p>
<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span><span class="p">[[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">]]</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">12</span><span class="p">])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>C√¢u l·ªánh n√†y s·∫Ω tr·∫£ v·ªÅ m·ªôt m·∫£ng m·ªôt chi·ªÅu g·ªìm c√°c ph·∫ßn t·ª≠: <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A[1][0]</code> v√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A[2][3]
</code>, t·ª©c <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">[1, 2]</code> v√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">[0, 3]</code> l√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">list</code> c√°c to·∫° ƒë·ªô theo m·ªói chi·ªÅu. Hai <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">list</code> n√†y 
ph·∫£i c√≥ ƒë·ªô d√†i b·∫±ng nhau ho·∫∑c m·ªôt <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">list</code> c√≥ ƒë·ªô d√†i b·∫±ng 1. 
Khi m·ªôt <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">list</code> c√≥ ƒë·ªô d√†i b·∫±ng 1, n√≥ s·∫Ω ƒë∆∞·ª£c <em>c·∫∑p</em> v·ªõi m·ªçi ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ c·ªßa <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">list</code> 
c√≤n l·∫°i. V√≠ d·ª•:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span><span class="p">[[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]]</span> <span class="c1"># equivalent to A[[1, 2], [0, 0]]
</span><span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">9</span><span class="p">])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<hr />

<p><strong>B√†i t·∫≠p:</strong> 
Vi·∫øt h√†m <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">myfunc</code> t√≠nh t·ªïng t·∫•t c·∫£ c√°c ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ c√≥ c·∫£ hai ch·ªâ s·ªë ƒë·ªÅu ch·∫µn c·ªßa 
m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code> b·∫•t k·ª≥. V√≠ d·ª•:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">8</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mi">9</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">10</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">11</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">12</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">myfunc</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="c1"># = 1 + 3 + 9 + 11
</span><span class="mi">24</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>G·ª£i √Ω: b·∫°n ƒë·ªçc t√¨m ƒë·ªçc tr∆∞·ªõc c√°ch s·ª≠ d·ª•ng <a href="https://docs.scipy.org/doc/numpy/reference/generated/numpy.sum.html"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">np.sum</code></a> cho m·∫£ng nhi·ªÅu chi·ªÅu.</p>

<hr />

<p><a name="-npsum-npmin-npmax-npmean-cho-mang-nhieu-chieu"></a></p>

<h2 id="26-npsum-npmin-npmax-npmean-cho-m·∫£ng-nhi·ªÅu-chi·ªÅu">2.6. np.sum, np.min, np.max, np.mean cho m·∫£ng nhi·ªÅu chi·ªÅu</h2>

<p>Xin nh·∫Øc l·∫°i v·ªÅ c√°ch quy ∆∞·ªõc <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">axis</code> c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n. <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">axis = 0</code> l√† t√≠nh theo chi·ªÅu 
t·ª´ tr√™n xu·ªëng d∆∞·ªõi, nghƒ©a l√† ph∆∞∆°ng c·ªßa n√≥ c√πng v·ªõi ph∆∞∆°ng c·ªßa c√°c c·ªôt. T∆∞∆°ng 
t·ª± <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">axis = 1</code> s·∫Ω c√≥ ph∆∞∆°ng c√πng v·ªõi ph∆∞∆°ng c·ªßa c√°c h√†ng. H√£y quan s√°t h√¨nh d∆∞·ªõi 
ƒë√¢y v√† ghi nh·ªõ c√°ch quy ∆∞·ªõc quan tr·ªçng n√†y.</p>

<hr />

<div class="imgcap">
<img src="/assets/fundaml/matrix.png" align="center" width="400" />
</div>
<hr />

<p>X√©t m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n:</p>
<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">numpy</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">np</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span> <span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">2.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">3.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">2.</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mf">4.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">3.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">7.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">4.</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">4.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">2.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">3.</span><span class="p">]])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>V√† c√°c h√†m <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">np.sum(), np.min(), np.max(), np.mean()</code> t√°c ƒë·ªông l√™n <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code> theo <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">axis = 0</code> (t·ª©c c√°c c·ªôt c·ªßa <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code>), k·∫øt qu·∫£ s·∫Ω l√†:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">sum</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">axis</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([</span>  <span class="mf">6.</span><span class="p">,</span>   <span class="mf">9.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">12.</span><span class="p">,</span>   <span class="mf">9.</span><span class="p">])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">min</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">axis</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([</span> <span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">2.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">2.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">2.</span><span class="p">])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">max</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">axis</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([</span> <span class="mf">4.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">4.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">7.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">4.</span><span class="p">])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">mean</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">axis</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([</span> <span class="mf">2.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">3.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">4.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">3.</span><span class="p">])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>C√°c gi√° tr·ªã theo c√°c h√†m tr√™ l·∫ßn l∆∞·ª£t l√† <em>t·ªïng, gi√° tr·ªã nh·ªè nh·∫•t, gi√° tr·ªã l·ªõn nh·∫•t, trung b√¨nh</em> theo m·ªói <strong>c·ªôt</strong>. K·∫øt qu·∫£ tr·∫£ v·ªÅ l√† c√°c m·∫£ng m·ªôt chi·ªÅu c√≥ s·ªë ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ b·∫±ng s·ªë c·ªôt c·ªßa <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code>.</p>

<p>T∆∞∆°ng t·ª± nh∆∞ th·∫ø khi thay <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">axis = 1</code>:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">sum</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">axis</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([</span>  <span class="mf">8.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">18.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">10.</span><span class="p">])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">min</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">axis</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([</span> <span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">3.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">max</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">axis</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([</span> <span class="mf">3.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">7.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">4.</span><span class="p">])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">mean</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">axis</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([</span> <span class="mf">2.</span> <span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">4.5</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">2.5</span><span class="p">])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>K·∫øt qu·∫£ tr·∫£ v·ªÅ ƒë∆∞·ª£c t√≠nh theo <strong>h√†ng</strong>. K·∫øt qu·∫£ tr·∫£ v·ªÅ c≈©ng l√† c√°c m·∫£ng m·ªôt 
chi·ªÅu c√≥ s·ªë ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ b·∫±ng v·ªõi s·ªë h√†ng c·ªßa A.</p>

<p>Khi kh√¥ng ƒë·ªÅ c·∫≠p t·ªõi <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">axis</code>, k·∫øt qu·∫£ ƒë∆∞·ª£c t√≠nh tr√™n to√†n b·ªô ma tr·∫≠n:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">sum</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="mf">36.0</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">min</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="mf">1.0</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">max</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="mf">7.0</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">mean</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="mf">3.0</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><a name="keepdims--true"></a></p>

<h3 id="keepdims--true"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">keepdims = True</code></h3>

<p>ƒê√¥i khi, ƒë·ªÉ thu·∫≠n ti·ªán cho vi·ªác t√≠nh to√°n v·ªÅ sau, ch√∫ng ta mu·ªën k·∫øt qu·∫£ tr·∫£ v·ªÅ khi <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">axis = 0</code> l√† c√°c vector h√†ng <strong>th·ª±c s·ª±</strong>, khi <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">axis = 1</code> l√† c√°c vector c·ªôt <strong>th·ª±c s·ª±</strong>.
ƒê·ªÉ l√†m ƒë∆∞·ª£c vi·ªác ƒë√≥, Numpy cung c·∫•p thu·ªôc t√≠nh <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">keepdims = True</code> (m·∫∑c ƒë·ªãnh l√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">False</code>). Khi <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">keepdims = True</code>, n·∫øu s·ª≠ d·ª•ng <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">axis = 0</code>, k·∫øt qu·∫£ s·∫Ω l√† m·ªôt m·∫£ng hai chi·ªÅu c√≥ chi·ªÅu th·ª© nh·∫•t b·∫±ng 1 (coi nh∆∞ ma tr·∫≠n m·ªôt h√†ng). 
T∆∞∆°ng t·ª±, n·∫øu s·ª≠ d·ª•ng <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">axis = 1</code>, k·∫øt qu·∫£ s·∫Ω l√† m·ªôt m·∫£ng hai chi·ªÅu c√≥ chi·ªÅu th·ª© hai b·∫±ng 1 (m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n c√≥ s·ªë c·ªôt b·∫±ng 1). Vi·ªác n√†y, v·ªÅ sau ch√∫ng ta s·∫Ω th·∫•y, quan tr·ªçng trong nhi·ªÅu tr∆∞·ªùng h·ª£p ƒë·∫∑c bi·ªát:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">sum</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">axis</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">keepdims</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">True</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span>  <span class="mf">6.</span><span class="p">,</span>   <span class="mf">9.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">12.</span><span class="p">,</span>   <span class="mf">9.</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">mean</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">axis</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">keepdims</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">True</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span> <span class="mf">2.</span> <span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mf">4.5</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mf">2.5</span><span class="p">]])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<hr />

<p><strong>B√†i t·∫≠p:</strong>
Cho m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code> b·∫•t k·ª≥. Trong m·ªói h√†ng, ta ƒë·ªãnh nghƒ©a <em>ƒë·ªô bi·∫øn ƒë·ªông</em> c·ªßa n√≥ 
l√† s·ª± kh√°c nhau gi·ªØa gi√° tr·ªã l·ªõn nh·∫•t v√† nh·ªè nh·∫•t c·ªßa c√°c ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ trong h√†ng 
ƒë√≥. H√£y vi·∫øt h√†m <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">myfunc</code> tr·∫£ v·ªÅ t·ªïng <em>ƒë·ªô bi·∫øn ƒë·ªông</em> c·ªßa t·∫•t c·∫£ c√°c h√†ng trong 
ma tr·∫≠n ƒë√≥.</p>

<p>V√≠ d·ª• v·ªõi ma tr·∫≠n <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code> trong b√†i h·ªçc, <em>ƒë·ªô bi·∫øn ƒë·ªông</em> c·ªßa m·ªói h√†ng l·∫ßn l∆∞·ª£t l√† 
<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">2.0, 4.0, 3.0</code>. V·∫≠y <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">myfunc(A) = 9.0</code>.</p>

<hr />

<p><a name="-cac-phep-toan-tac-dong-den-moi-phan-tu-cua-ma-tran"></a></p>

<h2 id="27-c√°c-ph√©p-to√°n-t√°c-ƒë·ªông-ƒë·∫øn-m·ªçi-ph·∫ßn-t·ª≠-c·ªßa-ma-tr·∫≠n">2.7. C√°c ph√©p to√°n t√°c ƒë·ªông ƒë·∫øn m·ªçi ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n</h2>

<p><a name="-tinh-toan-giua-mot-mang-hai-chieu-va-mot-so-vo-huong"></a></p>

<h3 id="271-t√≠nh-to√°n-gi·ªØa-m·ªôt-m·∫£ng-hai-chi·ªÅu-v√†-m·ªôt-s·ªë-v√¥-h∆∞·ªõng">2.7.1. T√≠nh to√°n gi·ªØa m·ªôt m·∫£ng hai chi·ªÅu v√† m·ªôt s·ªë v√¥ h∆∞·ªõng</h3>
<p>Khi t√≠nh to√°n gi·ªØa m·ªôt s·ªë v√¥ h∆∞·ªõng v√† m·ªôt m·∫£ng hai chi·ªÅu, v√≠ d·ª•:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">numpy</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">np</span> 
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="mi">2</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="mi">2</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">10</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="o">**</span><span class="n">A</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">8</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">32</span><span class="p">]])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>Ta nh·∫≠n th·∫•y r·∫±ng t·ª´ng ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ c·ªßa m·∫£ng s·∫Ω ƒë∆∞·ª£c k·∫øt h·ª£p v·ªõi s·ªë v√¥ h∆∞·ªõng b·∫±ng 
c√°c ph√©p to√°n t∆∞∆°ng ·ª©ng ƒë·ªÉ t·∫°o ra m·ªôt m·∫£ng m·ªõi c√πng k√≠ch th∆∞·ªõc. Vi·ªác n√†y, nh∆∞ 
c≈©ng ƒë√£ tr√¨nh b√†y trong khi l√†m vi·ªác v·ªõi m·∫£ng m·ªôt chi·ªÅu,
ƒë√∫ng v·ªõi c√°c m·∫£ng numpy v·ªõi s·ªë chi·ªÅu b·∫•t k·ª≥.</p>

<p><a name="-npabs-npsin-npexp-"></a></p>

<h3 id="272-npabs-npsin-npexp-">2.7.2. np.abs, np.sin, np.exp, ‚Ä¶</h3>
<p>B·∫°n ƒë·ªçc c≈©ng c√≥ th·ªÉ d·ª± ƒëo√°n ƒë∆∞·ª£c r·∫±ng c√°c h√†m s·ªë n√†y c≈©ng t√°c ƒë·ªông l√™n t·ª´ng 
ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ c·ªßa m·∫£ng v√† tr·∫£ v·ªÅ m·ªôt m·∫£ng c√πng k√≠ch th∆∞·ªõc v·ªõi m·∫£ng ban ƒë·∫ßu.</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">random</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">randn</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="c1"># create a random numpy array with shape = (2, 3)
</span><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span> <span class="mf">0.66079861</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">2.11481663</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="mf">1.42221111</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mf">1.13931439</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="mf">0.31866767</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="mf">0.37294795</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">abs</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span> <span class="mf">0.66079861</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">2.11481663</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">1.42221111</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mf">1.13931439</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">0.31866767</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">0.37294795</span><span class="p">]])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<hr />

<p><strong>B√†i t·∫≠p: Frobenious norm</strong></p>

<p><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Matrix_norm#Frobenius_norm">Frobenius norm</a> c·ªßa 
m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n ƒë∆∞·ª£c ƒë·ªãnh nghƒ©a l√† cƒÉn b·∫≠c hai c·ªßa t·ªïng b√¨nh ph∆∞∆°ng c√°c ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ c·ªßa 
ma tr·∫≠n. 
Frobenius norm ƒë∆∞·ª£c s·ª≠ d·ª•ng r·∫•t nhi·ªÅu trong c√°c thu·∫≠t to√°n Machine Learning v√¨ 
c√°c t√≠nh ch·∫•t to√°n h·ªçc ƒë·∫πp c·ªßa n√≥, trong ƒë√≥ quan tr·ªçng nh·∫•t l√† vi·ªác ƒë·∫°o h√†m c·ªßa 
b√¨nh ph∆∞∆°ng c·ªßa n√≥ r·∫•t ƒë∆°n gi·∫£n. 
Frobenius norm c·ªßa m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n \(\mathbf{A}\)
ƒë∆∞·ª£c k√Ω hi·ªáu l√† \(||\mathbf{A}||_F\)</p>

<p>Numpy c√≥ s·∫µn h√†m t√≠nh to√°n norm n√†y, tuy nhi√™n, ch√∫ng ta n√™n h·ªçc c√°ch t·ª± t√≠nh 
n√≥ tr∆∞·ªõc. 
Vi·∫øt h√†m <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">norm_fro(A)</code> t√≠nh Frobenius norm c·ªßa m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n b·∫•t k·ª≥.</p>

<p>V√≠ d·ª•:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">]])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>th√¨ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">norm_fro(A) = 6.2449979983983983</code> \(= \sqrt{1^2 + 3^2 + 2^2 + 5^2}\).</p>

<p><strong>G·ª£i √Ω:</strong> S·ª≠ d·ª•ng h√†m <a href="https://docs.scipy.org/doc/numpy-1.13.0/reference/generated/numpy.sqrt.html"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">np.sqrt</code></a>.</p>

<hr />

<p><a name="-cac-phep-toan-giua-hai-ma-tran-i"></a></p>

<h2 id="28-c√°c-ph√©p-to√°n-gi·ªØa-hai-ma-tr·∫≠n-i">2.8. C√°c ph√©p to√°n gi·ªØa hai ma tr·∫≠n I</h2>
<p>C√°c ph√©p to√°n c·ªông, tr·ª´, nh√¢n, chia, lu·ªπ th·ª´a (<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">+, -, *, /, **</code>) gi·ªØa hai m·∫£ng 
<strong>c√πng k√≠ch th∆∞·ªõc</strong> c≈©ng ƒë∆∞·ª£c th·ª±c hi·ªán d·ª±a tr√™n t·ª´ng c·∫∑p ph·∫ßn t·ª≠. K·∫øt qu·∫£ tr·∫£ 
v·ªÅ l√† m·ªôt m·∫£ng c√πng chi·ªÅu v·ªõi hai m·∫£ng ƒë√£ cho:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">numpy</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">np</span> 
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">B</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mf">5.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">8</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">B</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span>  <span class="mf">5.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">40.</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mf">14.</span><span class="p">,</span>   <span class="mf">9.</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span><span class="o">**</span><span class="n">B</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span>  <span class="mf">1.00000000e+00</span><span class="p">,</span>   <span class="mf">3.90625000e+05</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span>  <span class="mf">1.28000000e+02</span><span class="p">,</span>   <span class="mf">2.70000000e+01</span><span class="p">]])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><strong>Ch√∫ √Ω:</strong> t√≠ch c·ªßa hai ma tr·∫≠n nh∆∞ ƒë·ªãnh nghƒ©a trong ƒê·∫°i s·ªë tuy·∫øn t√≠nh ƒë∆∞·ª£c th·ª±c hi·ªán d·ª±a tr√™n h√†m s·ªë kh√°c. C√°ch vi·∫øt <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A*B</code> ƒë∆∞·ª£c th·ª±c hi·ªán tr√™n t·ª´ng c·∫∑p ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ c·ªßa <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code> v√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">B</code></p>

<hr />

<p><strong>B√†i t·∫≠p:</strong></p>

<p>Trong khi l√†m vi·ªác v·ªõi Machine Learning, ch√∫ng ta th∆∞·ªùng xuy√™n ph·∫£i <em>so s√°nh</em> hai ma tr·∫≠n. Xem xem li·ªáu ch√∫ng c√≥ g·∫ßn gi·ªëng nhau kh√¥ng. M·ªôt c√°ch ph·ªï bi·∫øn ƒë·ªÉ l√†m vi·ªác n√†y l√† t√≠nh b√¨nh ph∆∞∆°ng c·ªßa Frobineous norm
c·ªßa hi·ªáu hai ma tr·∫≠n ƒë√≥. C·ª• th·ªÉ, ƒë·ªÉ xem ma tr·∫≠n \(\mathbf{A}\) c√≥ g·∫ßn ma tr·∫≠n \(\mathbf{B}\) hay kh√¥ng, ng∆∞·ªùi ta th∆∞·ªùng t√≠nh \(||\mathbf{A} - \mathbf{B}||_F^2\).</p>

<p>Cho hai m·∫£ng hai chi·ªÅu c√≥ c√πng k√≠ch th∆∞·ªõc <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code> v√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">B</code>. Vi·∫øt h√†m <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">dist_fro</code> t√≠nh b√¨nh ph∆∞∆°ng Frobenious norm c·ªßa hi·ªáu hai ma tr·∫≠n ƒë∆∞·ª£c m√¥ t·∫£ b·ªüi hai m·∫£ng ƒë√≥.</p>

<hr />

<p><a name="-chuyen-vi-ma-tran-reshape-ma-tran"></a></p>

<h2 id="29-chuy·ªán-v·ªã-ma-tr·∫≠n-reshape-ma-tr·∫≠n">2.9. Chuy·ªán v·ªã ma tr·∫≠n, Reshape ma tr·∫≠n</h2>
<p><a name="-chuyen-vi-ma-tran"></a></p>

<h3 id="291-chuy·ªÉn-v·ªã-ma-tr·∫≠n">2.9.1 Chuy·ªÉn v·ªã ma tr·∫≠n</h3>

<p>C√≥ hai c√°ch ƒë·ªÉ l·∫•y chuy·ªÉn v·ªã c·ªßa m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n: d√πng thu·ªôc t√≠nh <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">.T</code> ho·∫∑c d√πng h√†m <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">np.transpose</code>:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">numpy</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">np</span> 
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">],[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">T</span> 
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">transpose</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">]])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><a name="-reshape"></a></p>

<h3 id="292-reshape">2.9.2. Reshape</h3>

<p>Khi l√†m vi·ªác v·ªõi ma tr·∫≠n, ch√∫ng ta s·∫Ω ph·∫£i th∆∞·ªùng xuy√™n l√†m vi·ªác v·ªõi c√°c ph√©p bi·∫øn ƒë·ªïi k√≠ch th∆∞·ªõc c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n. Ph√©p bi·∫øn ƒë·ªïi k√≠ch th∆∞·ªõc c√≥ th·ªÉ coi l√† vi·ªác s·∫Øp x·∫øp l·∫°i c√°c ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ c·ªßa m·ªôt 
ma tr·∫≠n v√†o m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n kh√°c c√≥ t·ªïng s·ªë ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ nh∆∞ nhau.</p>

<p>Trong numpy, ƒë·ªÉ l√†m ƒë∆∞·ª£c vi·ªác n√†y ch√∫ng ta d√πng ph∆∞∆°ng th·ª©c <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">.reshape</code> ho·∫∑c h√†m <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">np.reshape</code>. C√πng xem v√≠ d·ª•:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">reshape</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">))</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">reshape</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">]])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>S·ªë chi·ªÅu c·ªßa m·∫£ng m·ªõi kh√¥ng nh·∫•t thi·∫øt ph·∫£i b·∫±ng 2, n√≥ c√≥ th·ªÉ b·∫±ng b·∫•t k·ª≥ gi√° tr·ªã n√†o (l·ªõn h∆°n ho·∫∑c b·∫±ng 1) nh∆∞ng ph·∫£i ƒë·∫£m b·∫£o t·ªïng s·ªë ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ c·ªßa hai m·∫£ng l√† nh∆∞ nhau. Khi bi·∫øn th√†nh m·∫£ng 
m·ªôt chi·ªÅu, ta kh√¥ng d√πng tuple (nh∆∞ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">(3,2)</code>) n·ªØa m√† ch·ªâ d√πng m·ªôt s·ªë t·ª± nhi√™n:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">reshape</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="c1"># to a 1d numpy array
</span><span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">reshape</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="c1"># to a 3d numpy array 
</span><span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">]],</span>

       <span class="p">[[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">]],</span>

       <span class="p">[[</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">]]])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Ta c√≥ th·ªÉ nh·∫≠n th·∫•y r·∫±ng n·∫øu bi·∫øn th√†nh m·ªôt m·∫£ng hai chi·ªÅu m·ªõi, ta kh√¥ng nh·∫•t thi·∫øt ph·∫£i bi·∫øt k√≠ch th∆∞·ªõc c·ªßa m·ªói chi·ªÅu m√† ch·ªâ c·∫ßn k√≠ch th∆∞·ªõc c·ªßa m·ªôt chi·ªÅu. K√≠ch th∆∞·ªõc c√≤n l·∫°i ƒë∆∞·ª£c suy ra
t·ª´ vi·ªác t·ªïng s·ªë ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ c·ªßa hai m·∫£ng l√† nh∆∞ nhau. T∆∞∆°ng t·ª±, n·∫øu bi·∫øn th√†nh m·ªôt m·∫£ng ba chi·ªÅu m·ªõi, ta ch·ªâ c·∫ßn bi·∫øt hai trong ba k√≠ch th∆∞·ªõc. K√≠ch th∆∞·ªõc c√≤n l·∫°i s·∫Ω ƒë∆∞·ª£c python t·ª± t√≠nh ra, v√† ta
ch·ªâ c·∫ßn g√°n n√≥ b·∫±ng <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">-1</code>:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">reshape</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="c1"># to 1d array, its size must be 6
</span><span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">reshape</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">))</span> <span class="c1"># ~ a 2d array of shape 6x1
</span><span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">]])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><a name="-thu-tu-cua-phep-toan-reshape"></a></p>

<h3 id="293-th·ª©-t·ª±-c·ªßa-ph√©p-to√°n-reshape">2.9.3. Th·ª© t·ª± c·ªßa ph√©p to√°n reshape</h3>
<p>C√≥ m·ªôt ƒëi·ªÉm quan tr·ªçng c·∫ßn nh·ªõ l√† th·ª© t·ª± c·ªßa ph√©p to√°n reshape: c√°c ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ trong m·∫£ng m·ªõi ƒë∆∞·ª£c s·∫Øp x·∫øp nh∆∞ th·∫ø n√†o. C√≥ hai c√°ch s·∫Øp x·∫øp ch√∫ng ta c·∫ßn l∆∞u √Ω: m·∫∑c ƒë·ªãnh l√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">'C'-order</code>, v√† m·ªôt c√°ch kh√°c l√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">'F'-order</code> (xem h√¨nh).</p>

<hr />

<div class="imgcap">
<img src="assets/fundaml/reshape.png" align="center" width="400" />
</div>
<hr />

<p>Trong <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">'C'-order</code>, c√°c th√†nh ph·∫ßn c·ªßa m·∫£ng ngu·ªìn ƒë∆∞·ª£c qu√©t t·ª´ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">axis</code> <em>trong ra ngo√†i</em> (<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">axis = 1</code> r·ªìi m·ªõi t·ªõi <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">axis = 0</code> trong m·∫£ng hai chi·ªÅu, t·ª©c t·ª´ng h√†ng m·ªôt), sau ƒë√≥ ch√∫ng ƒë∆∞·ª£c x·∫øp v√†o m·∫£ng ƒë√≠ch c≈©ng theo th·ª© t·ª± ƒë√≥.</p>

<p>Trong <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">'F'-oder</code> (Fortran) c√°c th√†nh ph·∫ßn c·ªßa m·∫£ng ngu·ªìn ƒë∆∞·ª£c qu√©t t·ª´ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">axis</code> <em>ngo√†i v√†o trong</em> (trong m·∫£ng hai chi·ªÅu l√† t·ª´ng c·ªôt m·ªôt), sau ƒë√≥ ch√∫ng ƒë∆∞·ª£c s·∫Øp x·∫øp v√†o m·∫£ng ƒë√≠ch c≈©ng theo th·ª© t·ª± ƒë√≥ - t·ª´ng c·ªôt m·ªôt.</p>
<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">reshape</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">order</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">'F'</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> 

</code></pre></div></div>

<p>(ƒê·ªçc th√™m <a href="https://docs.scipy.org/doc/numpy/reference/generated/numpy.reshape.html"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">numpy.reshape</code></a>.)</p>

<hr />

<p><strong>B√†i t·∫≠p:</strong> 
H√£y t·∫°o ma tr·∫≠n <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code> sau m·ªôt c√°ch nhanh nh·∫•t, kh√¥ng d√πng c√°ch th·ªß c√¥ng ghi t·ª´ng ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ ra.</p>

<p>\[
\left[
\begin{matrix}
1 &amp;5&amp;9&amp;2\\6&amp;10&amp;3&amp;7 \\11&amp;4&amp;8&amp;12
\end{matrix}
\right]
\]
G·ª£i √Ω:</p>
<ul>
  <li>s·ª≠ d·ª•ng <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">np.arange()</code></li>
  <li>ƒê·ªÉ √Ω v·ªã tr√≠ c·ªßa 9, 10, 11 v√† 2, 3, 4</li>
  <li>L·ªùi gi·∫£i kh√¥ng qu√° hai d√≤ng</li>
</ul>

<p>B·∫°n c√≥ th·ªÉ nh·∫≠n ƒë∆∞·ª£c ph·∫£n h·ªìi ‚ÄòK·∫øt qu·∫£ th√†nh c√¥ng‚Äô nh∆∞ng h√£y th·ª≠ c·ªë nghƒ© quy lu·∫≠t c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n n√†y r·ªìi d√πng c√°c ph√©p <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">transpose, reshape</code> th√≠ch h·ª£p.</p>

<hr />

<p><a name="-cac-phep-toan-giua-ma-tran-va-vector"></a></p>

<h2 id="210-c√°c-ph√©p-to√°n-gi·ªØa-ma-tr·∫≠n-v√†-vector">2.10. C√°c ph√©p to√°n gi·ªØa ma tr·∫≠n v√† vector</h2>

<!-- *Ph·∫ßn t√≠ch gi·ªØa ma tr·∫≠n v√† vector trong ƒê·∫°i S·ªë Tuy·∫øn T√≠nh s·∫Ω ƒë∆∞·ª£c ƒë·ªÅ c·∫≠p ·ªü b√†i t·∫≠p sau*. -->

<p>Ch√∫ng ta ƒë√£ qua c√°c b√†i v·ªÅ ph√©p to√°n gi·ªØa m·ªôt m·∫£ng hai chi·ªÅu v√† m·ªôt s·ªë v√¥ h∆∞·ªõng, gi·ªØa hai m·∫£ng hai chi·ªÅu c√πng k√≠ch th∆∞·ªõc. Trong b√†i n√†y, ch√∫ng ta c√πng l√†m quen v·ªõi c√°c ph√©p to√°n gi·ªØa m·ªôt m·∫£ng hai chi·ªÅu 
v√† m·ªôt m·∫£ng m·ªôt chi·ªÅu. Tr∆∞·ªõc ti√™n, h√£y th·ª≠ v√†i v√≠ d·ª•:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">numpy</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">np</span> 
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">arange</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">12</span><span class="p">).</span><span class="n">reshape</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mi">8</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">9</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">10</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">11</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">b</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">b</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span>  <span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">,</span>   <span class="mf">3.</span><span class="p">,</span>   <span class="mf">5.</span><span class="p">,</span>   <span class="mf">8.</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span>  <span class="mf">5.</span><span class="p">,</span>   <span class="mf">7.</span><span class="p">,</span>   <span class="mf">9.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">12.</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span>  <span class="mf">9.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">11.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">13.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">16.</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">b</span> 
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span>  <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">,</span>   <span class="mf">2.</span><span class="p">,</span>   <span class="mf">6.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">15.</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span>  <span class="mf">4.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">10.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">18.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">35.</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span>  <span class="mf">8.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">18.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">30.</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mf">55.</span><span class="p">]])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Nh·∫≠n th·∫•y r·∫±ng k·∫øt qu·∫£ c·ªßa ph√©p to√°n <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A + b</code> thu ƒë∆∞·ª£c b·∫±ng c√°ch l·∫•y t·ª´ng <em>h√†ng</em> c·ªßa <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code> c·ªông v·ªõi <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">b</code>. K·∫øt qu·∫£ c·ªßa <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A*b</code> thu ƒë∆∞·ª£c b·∫±ng c√°ch l·∫•y t√≠ch c·ªßa t·ª´ng h√†ng c·ªßa <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code> v√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">b</code> - t√≠ch ·ªü ƒë√¢y l√† t√≠ch theo t·ª´ng ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ 
c·ªßa hai m·∫£ng m·ªôt chi·ªÅu, kh√¥ng ph·∫£i t√≠ch v√¥ h∆∞·ªõng c·ªßa hai vector. N√≥i c√°ch kh√°c, k·∫øt qu·∫£ c·ªßa <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A*b</code> thu ƒë∆∞·ª£c b·∫±ng c√°ch l·∫•y t·ª´ng <em>c·ªôt</em> c·ªßa <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code> nh√¢n v·ªõi ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ t∆∞∆°ng ·ª©ng c·ªßa <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">b</code>. Quy lu·∫≠t t∆∞∆°ng t·ª± x·∫£y ra 
v·ªõi c·∫£ ph√©p <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">-</code>, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">/</code> v√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">**</code>:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">c</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span><span class="o">**</span><span class="n">c</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span>  <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span>   <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span>   <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span>   <span class="mi">9</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span>  <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">25</span><span class="p">,</span>   <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">49</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span>  <span class="mi">8</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">81</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">10</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">121</span><span class="p">]])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<hr />

<p><strong>B√†i t·∫≠p</strong></p>

<p>Gi·∫£ s·ª≠ t·∫≠p d·ªØ li·ªáu bao g·ªìm nhi·ªÅu ƒëi·ªÉm d·ªØ li·ªáu c√≥ c√πng chi·ªÅu, ƒë∆∞·ª£c s·∫Øp x·∫øp th√†nh m·ªôt m·∫£ng hai chi·ªÅu m√¥ t·∫£ m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n - ƒë∆∞·ª£c g·ªçi l√† ma tr·∫≠n d·ªØ li·ªáu. M·ªói h√†ng c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n n√†y l√† m·ªôt ƒëi·ªÉm d·ªØ li·ªáu. 
M·ªôt trong c√°c k·ªπ thu·∫≠t quan tr·ªçng tr∆∞·ªõc khi √°p d·ª•ng c√°c thu·∫≠t to√°n Machine Learning l√™n d·ªØ li·ªáu l√† <a href="https://machinelearningcoban.com/general/2017/02/06/featureengineering/#feature-scaling-and-normalization"><strong>chu·∫©n ho√° d·ªØ li·ªáu</strong></a>.
Trong c√°c ph∆∞∆°ng ph√°p chu·∫©n ho√° d·ªØ li·ªáu, m·ªôt ph∆∞∆°ng ph√°p th∆∞·ªùng ƒë∆∞·ª£c s·ª≠ d·ª•ng l√† ƒë∆∞a d·ªØ li·ªáu v·ªÅ d·∫°ng <em>zero-mean</em>, t·ª©c trung b√¨nh c·ªông c·ªßa to√†n b·ªô d·ªØ li·ªáu l√† m·ªôt vector c√≥ to√†n b·ªô c√°c th√†nh ph·∫ßn b·∫±ng 0.</p>

<p>C√°ch chu·∫©n ho√° n√†y c√≥ th·ªÉ ƒë∆∞·ª£c th·ª±c hi·ªán b·∫±ng c√°ch tr∆∞·ªõc ti√™n t√≠nh vector trung b√¨nh c·ªßa to√†n b·ªô d·ªØ li·ªáu (·ªü ƒë√¢y l√† vector trung b√¨nh c·ªßa to√†n b·ªô c√°c h√†ng), 
sau ƒë√≥ l·∫•y t·ª´ng ƒëi·ªÉm d·ªØ li·ªáu tr·ª´ ƒëi vector trung b√¨nh. Khi ƒë√≥, ma tr·∫≠n m·ªõi s·∫Ω c√≥ trung b√¨nh c·ªông c√°c h√†ng b·∫±ng vector 0, v√† ta n√≥i r·∫±ng ma tr·∫≠n d·ªØ li·ªáu m·ªõi n√†y l√† <em>zero-mean</em>.</p>

<p>Cho m·ªôt m·∫£ng hai chi·ªÅu <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">X</code> m√¥ t·∫£ d·ªØ li·ªáu, trong ƒë√≥ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">X[i]</code> l√† m·ªôt m·∫£ng m·ªôt chi·ªÅu m√¥ t·∫£ d·ªØ li·ªáu c√≥ ch·ªâ s·ªë <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">i</code>. H√£y vi·∫øt h√†m <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">zero_mean</code> tr·∫£ v·ªÅ ma tr·∫≠n d·ªØ li·ªáu ƒë√£ chu·∫©n ho√° theo <em>zero-mean</em>.</p>

<hr />

<p><a name="-tich-giua-hai-ma-tran-tich-giua-ma-tran-va-vector"></a></p>

<h2 id="211-t√≠ch-gi·ªØa-hai-ma-tr·∫≠n-t√≠ch-gi·ªØa-ma-tr·∫≠n-v√†-vector">2.11. T√≠ch gi·ªØa hai ma tr·∫≠n, t√≠ch gi·ªØa ma tr·∫≠n v√† vector</h2>

<p><a name="-tich-giua-hai-ma-tran"></a></p>

<h3 id="2111-t√≠ch-gi·ªØa-hai-ma-tr·∫≠n">2.11.1. T√≠ch gi·ªØa hai ma tr·∫≠n</h3>
<p>Trong ƒê·∫°i S·ªë Tuy·∫øn T√≠nh (ƒêSTT), t√≠ch c·ªßa hai ma tr·∫≠n \(\mathbf{A} \in \mathbb{R}^{m\times n}\) v√† \(\mathbf{B} \in \mathbb{R}^{n \times p}\) ƒë∆∞·ª£c k√Ω hi·ªáu l√† \(\mathbf{C = AB} \in \mathbb{R}^{m \times p}\) 
trong ƒë√≥ ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ ·ªü h√†ng th·ª© \(i\) c·ªôt th·ª© \(j\) (t√≠nh t·ª´ \(0\)) c·ªßa \(\mathbf{C}\) ƒë∆∞·ª£c t√≠nh theo c√¥ng th·ª©c: 
\[
c_{ij} = \sum_{k=0}^{n-1}a_{ik}b_{kj}
\]</p>

<p>Ch√∫ √Ω r·∫±ng ƒë·ªÉ ph√©p nh√¢n th·ª±c hi·ªán ƒë∆∞·ª£c, s·ªë c·ªôt c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n th·ª© nh·∫•t ph·∫£i b·∫±ng v·ªõi s·ªë h√†ng c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n th·ª© hai (·ªü ƒë√¢y ƒë·ªÅu b·∫±ng \(n\)). V√† ph√©p nh√¢n ma tr·∫≠n kh√¥ng c√≥ t√≠nh ch·∫•t giao ho√°n, nh∆∞ng <strong>c√≥ t√≠nh ch·∫•t k·∫øt h·ª£p</strong>, t·ª©c: 
\[
\mathbf{ABC} = \mathbf{(AB)C} = \mathbf{A}(\mathbf{BC})
\]</p>

<p>Trong numpy, k√Ω hi·ªáu <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">*</code> kh√¥ng th·ª±c s·ª± ƒë·ªÉ ch·ªâ t√≠ch hai ma tr·∫≠n theo nghƒ©a n√†y m√† l√† t√≠ch theo t·ª´ng c·∫∑p ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ (element-wise). Ph√©p to√°n <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">*</code> trong numpy y√™u c·∫ßu hai m·∫£ng ph·∫£i c√≥ c√πng k√≠ch th∆∞·ªõc, v√† ph√©p to√°n n√†y c√≥ t√≠nh ch·∫•t giao ho√°n v√¨ ph√©p nh√¢n
c·ªßa hai s·ªë v√¥ h∆∞·ªõng c√≥ t√≠nh ch·∫•t giao ho√°n.</p>

<p>Cho hai m·∫£ng numpy hai chi·ªÅu <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A, B</code> trong ƒë√≥ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A.shape[1] == B.shape[0]</code> (ƒë·ª´ng qu√™n ƒëi·ªÅu ki·ªán n√†y). N·∫øu hai m·∫£ng n√†y m√¥ t·∫£ hai ma tr·∫≠n th√¨ t√≠ch c·ªßa hai ma tr·∫≠n (theo ƒêSTT) c√≥ th·ªÉ ƒë∆∞·ª£c th·ª±c hi·ªán b·∫±ng thu·ªôc t√≠nh 
<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">.dot</code> ho·∫∑c h√†m <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">np.dot</code>:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">numpy</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">np</span> 
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">arange</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">12</span><span class="p">).</span><span class="n">reshape</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">8</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mi">9</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">10</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">11</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">B</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">arange</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">).</span><span class="n">reshape</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">B</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">dot</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">B</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span>  <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span>   <span class="mi">8</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">11</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">14</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span>   <span class="mi">8</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">20</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">32</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">13</span><span class="p">,</span>   <span class="mi">8</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">29</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">50</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">22</span><span class="p">,</span>   <span class="mi">8</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">38</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">68</span><span class="p">]])</span>
