<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="mi">11</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">35</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">59</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">83</span><span class="p">])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">A</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">b</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([[</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="mi">8</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">12</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">20</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">21</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">32</span><span class="p">],</span>
       <span class="p">[</span> <span class="mi">9</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">30</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">44</span><span class="p">]])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>T√≠ch c·ªßa m·∫£ng hai chi·ªÅu <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code> v√† m·∫£ng m·ªôt chi·ªÅu <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">b</code> v·ªõi <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A.shape[1] == b.shape[0]</code> theo ƒêSTT ƒë∆∞·ª£c th·ª±c hi·ªán b·∫±ng ph∆∞∆°ng th·ª©c <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">.dot()</code> c·ªßa m·∫£ng numpy <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code>. K·∫øt qu·∫£ tr·∫£ v·ªÅ l√† m·ªôt m·∫£ng m·ªôt chi·ªÅu c√≥ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">shape[0] == 4</code>. 
Ch√∫ng ta c·∫ßn ch√∫ √Ω m·ªôt ch√∫t ·ªü ƒë√¢y l√† k·∫øt qu·∫£ tr·∫£ v·ªÅ l√† m·ªôt m·∫£ng m·ªôt chi·ªÅu ch·ª© kh√¥ng ph·∫£i m·ªôt vector c·ªôt (ƒë∆∞·ª£c bi·ªÉu di·ªÖn b·ªüi m·ªôt m·∫£ng hai chi·ªÅu c√≥ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">shape[1] = 1</code>) nh∆∞ tr√™n l√Ω thuy·∫øt. K·∫øt qu·∫£
c·ªßa <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A*b</code> c≈©ng ƒë∆∞·ª£c ch·ªâ ra ƒë·ªÉ nh·∫Øc c√°c b·∫°n ph√¢n bi·ªát hai ph√©p nh√¢n n√†y.</p>

<p>Ti·∫øp t·ª•c quan s√°t:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">b</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">dot</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">Traceback</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">most</span> <span class="n">recent</span> <span class="n">call</span> <span class="n">last</span><span class="p">):</span>
  <span class="n">File</span> <span class="s">"&lt;stdin&gt;"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">line</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">module</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
<span class="nb">ValueError</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">shapes</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,)</span> <span class="ow">and</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="ow">not</span> <span class="n">aligned</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="mi">3</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">dim</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">!=</span> <span class="mi">4</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">dim</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">c</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">])</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">c</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">dot</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="mi">60</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">70</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">80</span><span class="p">])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>ta th·∫•y r·∫±ng n·∫øu ƒë·∫∑t <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">b</code> l√™n tr∆∞·ªõc <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code> th√¨ c√≥ l·ªói x·∫£y ra v√¨ xung ƒë·ªôt chi·ªÅu. Tuy nhi√™n n·∫øu m·∫£ng m·ªôt chi·ªÅu <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">c</code> c√≥ k√≠ch th∆∞·ªõc b·∫±ng <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">4</code> th√¨ l·∫°i c√≥ th·ªÉ nh√¢n v·ªõi m·∫£ng hai chi·ªÅu <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code> ƒë∆∞·ª£c. 
K·∫øt qu·∫£ thu ƒë∆∞·ª£c ch√≠nh l√† vector h√†ng <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">c</code> nh√¢n v·ªõi ma tr·∫≠n <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code>. (B·∫°n c√≥ th·ªÉ t·ª± ki·ªÉm tra l·∫°i).</p>

<p>C√≥ m·ªôt ch√∫t c·∫ßn l∆∞u √Ω ·ªü ƒë√¢y: N·∫øu m·∫£ng m·ªôt chi·ªÅu ƒë∆∞·ª£c nh√¢n v√†o sau m·ªôt m·∫£ng hai chi·ªÅu, n√≥ ƒë∆∞·ª£c coi nh∆∞ m·ªôt vector c·ªôt. N·∫øu n√≥ ƒë∆∞·ª£c nh√¢n v√†o tr∆∞·ªõc m·ªôt m·∫£ng hai chi·ªÅu, n√≥ l·∫°i ƒë∆∞·ª£c coi l√† m·ªôt vector h√†ng. 
D√π sao th√¨ n√≥ v·∫´n l√† m·ªôt vector, v√† v·∫´n ƒë∆∞·ª£c l∆∞u b·ªüi m·ªôt m·∫£ng m·ªôt chi·ªÅu :). ƒê√¢y c≈©ng ch√≠nh l√† m·ªôt trong nh·ªØng l√Ω o m√† nh·ªØng ng∆∞·ªùi ban ƒë·∫ßu l√†m quen v·ªõi numpy g·∫∑p nhi·ªÅu kh√≥ khƒÉn.</p>

<hr />

<p><strong>B√†i t·∫≠p:</strong> Quay l·∫°i v·ªõi Frobineus norm. C√≥ m·ªôt c√°ch kh√°c ƒë·ªÉ t√≠nh b√¨nh ph∆∞∆°ng c·ªßa Frobineus norm c·ªßa m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n d·ª±a tr√™n c√¥ng th·ª©c: 
\[
||\mathbf{A}||_F^2 = \text{trace}(\mathbf{AA}^T) = \text{trace}(\mathbf{A}^T\mathbf{A})
\]</p>

<p>trong ƒë√≥ \(\text{trace}()\) l√† h√†m t√≠nh t·ªïng c√°c ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ tr√™n ƒë∆∞·ªùng ch√©o c·ªßa m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n vu√¥ng.</p>

<p>Cho m·ªôt m·∫£ng hai chi·ªÅu <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code>, h√£y vi·∫øt h√†m <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">fro_trace</code> t√≠nh b√¨nh ph∆∞∆°ng c·ªßa Frobineus norm c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n n√†y d·ª±a v√†o c√¥ng th·ª©c tr√™n.</p>

<p>G·ª£i √Ω:</p>
<ul>
  <li>s·ª≠ d·ª•ng h√†m <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">np.diag</code>, ho·∫∑c</li>
  <li>s·ª≠ d·ª•ng <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">np.trace</code> (g√µ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">help(np.trace)</code> tr√™n Terminal ho·∫∑c google ƒë·ªÉ bi·∫øt th√™m chi ti·∫øt).</li>
</ul>

<p>Hy v·ªçng c√°c b·∫°n g·∫∑p kh√≥ khƒÉn ch√∫t v·ªõi Compiler v√† nh·∫≠n ra l√Ω do c·ªßa vi·ªác ƒë√≥ ;).</p>

<hr />

<p><a name="-softmax-iii---phien-ban-tong-quat"></a></p>

<h2 id="212-softmax-iii---phi√™n-b·∫£n-t·ªïng-qu√°t">2.12. Softmax III - Phi√™n b·∫£n t·ªïng qu√°t</h2>
<p>Ch√∫ng ta ƒë√£ l√†m quen v·ªõi <a href="https://fundaml.com/course/5990a766cdc6e32b3b4d0666/lesson/5990aa22cdc6e32b3b4d0667/5991da2ecdc6e32b3b4d066e">Phi√™n b·∫£n ·ªïn ƒë·ªãnh c·ªßa h√†m Softmax</a>
v·ªõi m·ªôt m·ªôt m·∫£ng m·ªôt chi·ªÅu \(\mathbf{z}\):</p>

\[\frac{\exp(z_i)}{\sum_{j=0}^{C-1} \exp(z_j)} = 
\frac{\exp(-b)\exp(z_i)}{\exp(-b)\sum_{j=0}^{C-1} \exp(z_j)}
= \frac{\exp(z_i-b)}{\sum_{j=0}^{C-1} \exp(z_j-b)}\]

<p>B√¢y gi·ªù, ch√∫ng ta ti·∫øp t·ª•c t·ªïng qu√°t h√†m s·ªë n√†y ƒë·ªÉ √°p d·ª•ng cho nhi·ªÅu ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ 
c√πng l√∫c. Gi·∫£ s·ª≠ ma tr·∫≠n \(\mathbf{Z}\) l√† ma tr·∫≠n <em>scores</em> c·ªßa \(N\) ƒëi·ªÉm d·ªØ 
li·ªáu, m·ªói h√†ng \(\mathbf{z}_i\) c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n n√†y ·ª©ng v·ªõi score c·ªßa m·ªôt ƒëi·ªÉm d·ªØ li·ªáu. 
H√£y vi·∫øt m·ªôt h√†m s·ªë tr√™n python ƒë·ªÉ t√≠nh softmax cho t·ª´ng h√†ng c·ªßa \(\mathbf{Z}\). 
K·∫øt qu·∫£ thu ƒë∆∞·ª£c l√† m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n \(\mathbf{A}\) c√πng chi·ªÅu v·ªõi \(\mathbf{Z}\) m√† 
m·ªói h√†ng c·ªßa \(\mathbf{A}\) l√† k·∫øt qu·∫£ khi √°p d·ª•ng h√†m Softmax l√™n m·ªôt h√†ng t∆∞∆°ng 
·ª©ng c·ªßa \(\mathbf{Z}\).</p>

<p>B·∫°n ƒë·ªçc c·∫ßn vi·∫øt h√†m d∆∞·ªõi d·∫°ng <em>vectorization</em>, t·ª©c kh√¥ng s·ª≠ d·ª•ng v√≤ng <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">for</code>.</p>

<p><strong>G·ª£i √Ω:</strong> L·ªùi gi·∫£i c√≥ th·ªÉ kh√¥ng v∆∞·ª£t qu√° 2 d√≤ng l·ªánh.</p>
:ET